Package org.dalesbred.results

Handling database-results.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ResultSetProcessor<T>
    Callback for processing a whole ResultSet.
    RowMapper<T>
    Maps a single row of result-set into an object.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ListWithRowMapperResultSetProcessor<T>
    A ResultSetProcessor that creates a list of results using given RowMapper.
    MapResultSetProcessor<K,V>
    ResultSetProcessor that expects results with two columns and creates map from them.
    ReflectionResultSetProcessor<T>
    Builds a list of results from ResultSet using reflection to instantiate individual rows.
    ResultTableResultSetProcessor
    Creates a ResultTable from ResultSet.
    UniqueResultSetProcessor<T>
    A ResultSetProcessor that adapts another a list-producing processor to produce only single result.
